{"tid":1362774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]《大公報》頭版譴責港鐵","createTime":"2019-07-25T03:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:50:58.000Z","uid":109379,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ef28e69fada0be8753a081a0399d116df6814d","tid":1362774,"uid":109379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"《大公報》﹣ 廢青癱港鐵 害慘全城<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>搞事分子</strong></span>一連兩日搗亂港鐵運作，120班列車受阻，連累10萬計打工仔上班遲到。昨早八時上班繁忙時段，十多名戴口罩及黑衣人在金鐘站故意阻礙車門關閉，30列列車受阻5至27分鐘不等，多個車站迫爆候車乘客，的士站亦大排長龍。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有上班市民不滿搞事者「阻人返工」，直斥他們破壞社會秩序</strong></span>，最終警方將搞事者拖出車外，列車服務於早上9時15分起恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n大公報今日炒晒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日份頭版改個日期又用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cc351ce0b93ff79c2080606c50b86911780cc9","tid":1362774,"uid":280080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"[跪求幫推！非標題黨！！] 727前，文宣巴絲一定要做好嘅準備功夫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dppQeT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dppQeT</a>"},{"pid":"bdb027213c6dae9796c3fa5b959ff2a422acf694","tid":1362774,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"顧掂自己個招牌先啦 傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6918f7cad1a1fff2c7677a093e29a7dc0734a66","tid":1362774,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"大律師公會前主席石永泰促請政府成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362836</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}